snippet.title: Coria and the Sunken City - Animated Trailer
snippet.description:
How did Coria arrive at the mysterious Agoe Island? Follow the first steps of the upcoming Game Boy / Game Boy Color game's heroine in this animated trailer.

Animation: Nika Gorev - https://twitter.com/Machaon_chan
Music: Sebastian Sonntag -https:// twitter.com/seb_sonntag

Find a playable demo at https://coria.itch.io/coria
Follow us at https://twitter.com/CoriaGameBoy
If you´re interested in the creation of the trailer, go to https://coria.itch.io/coria/devlog/231075/trailer-talk
